    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/fa09f23c2df0d5300aa9f6a6591cf251.poster.avif?t=1701573279\" width=615 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/fa09f23c2df0d5300aa9f6a6591cf251.webm?t=1701573279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 这是一款硬核街机风格游戏，专注于快速和基于技能的游戏玩法以及身临其境的视听效果。          </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 它依赖于一种简单、直观的控制方案，让玩家能够快速掌握游戏机制。          </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/6548c28167e6b97c9a4f770eb2a8797b.poster.avif?t=1701573279\" width=614 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/6548c28167e6b97c9a4f770eb2a8797b.webm?t=1701573279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/6548c28167e6b97c9a4f770eb2a8797b.mp4?t=1701573279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>该游戏具有一系列越来越具有挑战性的关卡，需要玩家利用自己的反应能力和时机来克服障碍。 游戏的玩法非常容易上瘾，因为玩家努力提高自己的技能并打破自己的高分。 该游戏具有身临其境的配乐和出色的图形设计<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/62bb24984f168a74802adf5081121ce9.avif?t=1701573279\" width=615 height=243 /></span>",
